### Criar novo pedido
POST http://localhost:3000/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientName": "João Silva",
  "dentistName": "Dr. Maria Santos",
  "services": ["Coroa de Porcelana", "Implante Dentário"],
  "totalValue": 2500.00,
  "deadline": "2026-02-15"
}

###

### Listar todos os pedidos
GET http://localhost:3000/api/orders

###

### Listar pedidos com filtros e paginação
GET http://localhost:3000/api/orders?state=ANALYSIS&page=1&limit=10

###

### Buscar pedido por ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/orders/REPLACE_WITH_ORDER_ID

###

### Atualizar pedido
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/orders/REPLACE_WITH_ORDER_ID
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "totalValue": 2800.00,
  "deadline": "2026-02-20"
}

###

### Avançar estado do pedido
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/orders/REPLACE_WITH_ORDER_ID/advance

###

### Deletar pedido
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/orders/REPLACE_WITH_ORDER_ID

###

### Obter estatísticas
GET http://localhost:3000/api/orders/stats

###

### Health check
GET http://localhost:3000/api/health
